23
00:02:10,087 --> 00:02:11,171
C'est mon ami.

24
00:02:11,338 --> 00:02:12,549
Tu vas rater le tour.

25
00:02:13,049 --> 00:02:14,384
Vas-y.

26
00:02:21,265 --> 00:02:24,102
